          %p
            %strong Your Choices Regarding Your Personal Information
          %p
            At any time you may stop us from contacting you for marketing purposes. When you receive
            promotional communications from us, you may indicate a preference to stop receiving further
            promotional communications and you will have the opportunity to "opt-out" by following the
