          %p
            %strong Feedback
          %p
            If you contact us to provide comments, we may use and disclose your comments for any purpose,
            provided that we do not associate the comments to your Personal Information.  You agree that
            any such comments and any email we receive becomes our property. We may use feedback for marketing
