          %p
            %strong Security
          %p
            We use a variety of industry standard security technologies to insure that you Personal
            Information is protected.  While we strive for perfection, be advised that no company,
            including Optyn can fully eliminate 100% of security risks.
          %p
            %strong Contact And Revisions
          %p
            If you have questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
            %strong info@optyn.com.
          %p
